0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:29:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">全球「和尼畫」<br />\n#XinniethePooh Challenge</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rG1sQ5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrG1sQ5b.jpg&h=d6b3d577&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9NvORS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9NvORS.jpg&h=fcaaa2a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「和尼畫」挑戰<br />\n1.畫出你心中所想的維尼圖<br />\n2.留下你想對習維尼講嘅說話<br />\n3.放上ig、fb、twitter，tag #XinniethePooh<br />\n4.tag 1-3個你想佢一齊畫維尼嘅朋友<br />\n5.被tag嘅朋友一齊畫維尼，讓愛與維尼佔領地球，推到畀習維尼本人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot; Challenge<br />\n1. Draw your own &quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot;<br />\n2. Write down what do you want to tell Chairman Xi<br />\n3. Post your work on ig, fb and twitter with tag #Xinniethepooh <br />\n4. Tag up to 3 more friends to draw together!"},{"pid":"3f389cbe91386c3643346b3384451fe0215d15a1","tid":1641302,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:46:01.000Z","msg":"我都上唔到"},{"pid":"371dda0f7e64d3c398934c9ae84e5ac9dde7d15d","tid":1641302,"uid":271759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:48:30.000Z","msg":"維尼熊&quot;被消失&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}